    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a title=\"PZO1121\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1601253907/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1601253907&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO1121</a></p>\r\n<p>Blight tonic increases the potency of a creature's <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/diseases\">disease</a> attack transmitted by physical contact, such as a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/animals/rat/dire-rat\">dire rat's</a> filth fever. The next time a creature must save against the drinker's <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/diseases\">disease</a> save DC, the DC for the initial infection increases by +2. The tonic lasts for 10 minutes or until the next time a creature must save against the drinker's <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/diseases\">disease</a> DC, whichever comes first.</p>\r\n",
